Sentencas: Microreactors are composed of channels with a dimension of 1-1000 mum in width and depth.
Titulo: Simulation of membrane microreactor for fuel cell with methane feed

Sentencas: Three types of membrane microreactors for production of electric power by fuel cells with methane feed, i.e. (1) Pd membrane microreactor (Pd-MMR) followed by polymer electrolyte fuel cell (PEFC), (2) oxide-ion conducting solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) and (3) proton conducting solid oxide fuel cell (H+-SOFC) were simulated and compared.
Titulo: Simulation of membrane microreactor for fuel cell with methane feed

Sentencas: The Pd-MMR followed by PEFC was the most effective system for electric power generation compared with the other two types of SOFC although the system was rather complex.
Titulo: Simulation of membrane microreactor for fuel cell with methane feed

Sentencas: However, the performances were dependent on the permeation properties of membranes (Pd, YSZ, perovskite) as well as kinetics of catalysts.
Titulo: Simulation of membrane microreactor for fuel cell with methane feed
